{"success":true,"message":"操作成功","code":200,"subCode":"","result":{"id":"209","name":"地址级别判断","path":null,"personDayQuato":null,"enterpriseDayQuato":null,"personMinQuato":null,"enterpriseMinQuato":null,"personMonthQuato":null,"enterpriseMonthQuato":null,"personSumQuato":null,"enterpriseSumQuato":null,"code":null,"certificationNeeded":null,"description":null,"owner":null,"firstType":0,"serviceType":1,"secondType":null,"status":2,"requestType":0,"special":0,"applicationType":0,"innerUrl":null,"outerUrl":null,"wordContext":"# 地址级别判断\n\n## 接口说明\n\n判断输入地址的精细度、是否详细、是否存在地址冲突，可用于重要函证寄递、企业商事登记核实等业务场景。\n\n## API服务地址\n```txt\nhttps://gis-apis.sf-express.com/iad/api\n请求方式：GET\n```\n\n## 请求参数\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>参数名</th>\n            <th>类型</th>\n            <th>必需</th>\n            <th>描述</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>address</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>是</td>\n            <td>详细地址</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>province</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n            <td>省信息，中文</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>city</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n            <td>城市信息，中文</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>county</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n            <td>区县信息，中文</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>town</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n            <td>镇(街道)信息，中文</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>ak</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>是</td>\n            <td>用户申请的授权码</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n### 请求示例\n\n``````json\n{\n    \"address\": \"深圳市软件产业基地\",\n    \"province\": \"广东省\",\n    \"city \": \"深圳市\",\n\t  \"county\": \"南山区\",\n\t  \"town\": \"后海街道\"\n}\n``````\n## 返回参数\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th colspan=\"3\">参数</th>\n            <th>类型</th>\n            <th>描述</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"3\">status</td>\n            <td>number</td>\n            <td>状态码:0-成功，1-失败</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"3\">result</td>\n            <td>object</td>\n            <td>结果数据集</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">query</td>\n            <td>object</td>\n            <td>查询参数集</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>address</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>请求查询的地址</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>province</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>省</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>city</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>市</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>county</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>区(县)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>town</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>镇(街道)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">data</td>\n            <td>object</td>\n            <td>响应数据集</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>explicit</td>\n            <td>integer</td>\n            <td>\n                地址是否详细：0 不详细；1 详细\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>multi</td>\n            <td>integer</td>\n            <td>\n                0：省市区无冲突；1：多省冲突，如广东省广西省xxx；2：多市冲突，如广东省深圳市东莞市xxx；11：省市冲突，如：广东省杭州市xxx；22：市区冲突（区在省内），如：广东省广州市南山区xxx；33：省区冲突（区在省外），如：浙江省杭州市南山区xxx\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>level</td>\n            <td>integer</td>\n            <td>\n                分词精细级别\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">sn</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>结果标识sn码</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n### 返回示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": 0,\n  \"result\": {\n    \"query\": {\n      \"address\": \"上海上海市宝山区蕴川路1800弄3号永富堆场\"\n    },\n    \"data\": {\n      \"explicit\": 1,\n      \"level\": 13,\n      \"multi\": \"0\",\n    },\n    \"sn\": \"0000942023102318372263022502\"\n  }\n}\n```","requestExample":null,"price":null,"responseExample":null,"createUser":"admin-op","updateUser":"admin-op","updateTime":"2026-01-12 10:13:20","createTime":"2025-12-18 23:33:59","pageNo":1,"pageSize":10,"statusList":null,"isTrial":null,"sort":1,"accessScope":null,"accessUser":null,"serviceConfigs":null,"deleteServiceConfigIds":null,"type":2,"pid":"122","deleted":0,"personUsageDays":null,"enterpriseUsageDays":null},"any":{}}